g.text: Ron's wand is probably somewhere on the ground near the school Owlery: Ron dropped his wand on the way back from a Quidditch match, almost certainly held at the school Quidditch pitch, but before entering the school castle1. According to Ginny, they were heading towards Gryffindor tower most of the way back, and according to George, they passed nearby a building to their left1. A map of the school grounds shows that if one were heading from the pitch towards the tower, the nearest building to the left would be the Owlery.21./Floochat.hog.net/weasleybunch/2./Comp.hog.net/albusd-pc/#schoollayoutppt
